(264, 'en', 'Contact Us', NULL, '<h2 style="text-align:center"><u>Head Office</u></h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. Ministry of Post and Telecommunication.&nbsp;Phone number: 021215877</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>2. Personnel Department.&nbsp;Phone number: 021218720, 021222972</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>3. Department of Planning and Cooperation.&nbsp;Phone number: 021219902</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>4. Finance Department.&nbsp;Phone number: 021241180</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>Email:&nbsp;<a href="http://info@mpt.gov.la" style="font-size: 13px;">info@mpt.gov.la</a></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:center"><a href="http://www.google.la/maps/place/Ministry+of+Posts+and+Telecommunications/@17.9645199,102.612352,18z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x3124688782a4f6bb:0x219b7a18fdbfd675!8m2!3d17.964399!4d102.6125481?hl=th"><img alt="" src="/files/Untitled.jpg" style="height:396px; width:707px" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style="text-align:center"><u>Km3 Office</u></h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. E-Government Center. Phone number: 021316600</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>2. Institute of Information and Communication Technology. Phone number: 021312427</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>3. Department of Information and Communication technology. Phone number: 021316563</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>4. Lao Telecommunications Regulatory Authority. Phone number: 021316560</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>5. Information and Communications Regulation TechnologyPromotion.&nbsp;Phone number: 021316562</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>6. Department of Post. Phone number: 021315115</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>7. Inspection Department.&nbsp;Phone number: 021316550, 021316536</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:center"><a href="https://www.google.la/maps/place/Institute+of+Posts+and+Telecommunications/@17.9390643,102.6231289,16.75z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x0:0x4fa049f096fb6b3c!8m2!3d17.9394498!4d102.6235431?hl=th"><img alt="" src="/files/1.JPG" style="height:438px; width:707px" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:center"