(13, 'Alesarhisp', 'wpbihlardEdgermedurl@greenslots2017.co', 'dakota sioux casino', 'http://dkjshye7s632.com \r\nAw, this was a really nice post. In idea I would like to put in writing like this additionally – taking time and actual effort to make an excellent article… but what can I say… I procrastinate alot and on no account appear to get something done.\r\n', '86976125399', '', 3, '2018-03-21 12:05:58'),
