(15, 'Naoto Sumiyoshi', 'Jp.company001@gmail.com', 'Drone flights rules in Laos', 'I am writing to you for the request of information about drone flights rules in Laos.\r\n \r\nNext February, I will visit Laos and would like to operate small drone (weight 900g). I will not operate near airport, but I would like to know rules and laws in Laos for avoid any troubles in advance.\r\n \r\nMy drone flights conditions will;\r\n\r\nNot near airport.\r\nOnly fly at tourism areas in Vientiane, Luang Prabang, and Champasack  (Rural areas).\r\nNot commercial use, but recreational purpose\r\nBelow 100m altitude\r\n900g weight DJI Mavic 2\r\nMy total drone flight time experiences are 905 hours \r\nMy drone has camera, I will take photos and movies for recreational purposes.\r\nAbove conditions, if there needs permission from relevant authorities, I would like to take the permission. Would you please inform the procedures.\r\n \r\nYour support in this respect is greatly appreciated.\r\n \r\nSincerely,\r\n \r\nNaoto Sumiyoshi (Mr.)\r\nKonan Minato-Ku Tokyo, Japan\r\ne-mail: jp.company001@gmail.com', '', '', 1, '2018-12-27 05:59:20'),
(16, 'ຈອນສິນ ', 'johnsin.oudomvilay@hotmail.com', 'ມາດຕາ 3 ການອະທິບາຍຄຳສັບ ຂອງກົດໝາຍໄປສະນີ ເລກທີ 45/ສພຊ ລົງວັນທີ 25/12/2014', 'ຄຳວ່າໂລຊິດສະຕິກໄປສະນີໝາຍເຖິງຫຍັງ? ຊ່ວຍອະທິບາຍ ແລະ ຍົກຕົວຢ່າງໃຫ້ເບິ່ງແນ່? ຂອບໃຈ', '02059985886', '', 3, '2019-01-02 05:42:48'),
(17, 'NTEK Consult', 'john.jiang@ntek.org.cn', 'MPT consults', 'Dear SIR:\r\n I am John of NTEK,one of Chinese test lab,sometimes,we have some MPT consults,but i donot know the process of the MPT,can you send me MPT guide and introduce,and i can follow the guide apply the documents,thank you very much', '86 0755 61156542', 'issue_2019010412015743.pdf', 1, '2019-01-04 12:43:57'),
(18, 'chittaphone', 'chittaphone@gmail.com', 'test comment', 'test comment', '', '', 1, '2019-01-10 03:17:07'),
(19, 'ສັກດາລີ', 'sakdaly@gmail.com', ' ດາວໂຫລດນິຕິກຳຕ່າງໆ  ', 'ບ່ອນດາວໂຫລດນິຕິກຳຕ່າງໆ ຂອງກະຊວງ ບໍ່ເຫັນຄືເມື່ອກ່ອນ, ມີແຕ່ຊ່ອງເຜີຍແຜ່ເອກະສານໃໝ່,', '55534564', '', 3, '2019-01-10 08:10:25'),
(20, 'Marvin Scholz', 'marvinscholz.ms@outlook.de', 'Drone Permission', 'Hello, I want to get a drone permission for my DJI Mavic Air while my journey in Laos. Please contact me \r\n\r\nYours sincerely \r\nMarvin Scholz', '+491622916766', '', 1, '2019-01-16 02:52:26'),
